rComments: Great Prof! Very understanding and great to talk to. Tries to make dry material fun and exams are reasonable. good person, good prof.

My favorite prof this year. Slides are clear, organized, and online ahead of time. + exams are based on book so you don't have to go to class if you don't want to. But you want to, because she shows interesting movies and youtube videos, does activities, true or false trivia, class discussions, etc. It's actually fun.
I loved this professor! She was so positive, so kind, so good at helping us see the relevance of the material for our lives and the world. Take her if you can.
